{"tid":2063090,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［失戀］女朋友對我已經冇左信任","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:45:28.000Z","uid":318946,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"16f676ef3a9c99ab6ab0377548a0b050d93ee264","tid":2063090,"uid":318946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"自介下<br />\n<br />\n廿出頭，A380，以前好中意同班損友吹鹹濕野，咩都吹下，又sp又叫雞又hehe咁，但我只係毒撚只係吹下水，有咁大吹咁大，冇做過d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到識左個女朋友之後想定落黎，focus哂佢身上，基本上斷哂班損友聯絡，因為佢對我好好，我都好中意佢，大家都好夾，成日糖黐豆咁，半年都係熱戀期。<br />\n<br />\n但係比佢發現左我d鹹濕對話記錄，佢覺得我對唔住佢，好有可疑，信唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，我應該點做，我唔想就咁完，好難得先搵到個岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a9e7e991bbd836006f2b6c41c90fa2e6525b03","tid":2063090,"uid":299468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"承諾同行動<br />\n最緊要後者<br />\n比佢睇到你有明顯改變<br />\n因為如果我係佢角度<br />\n我都會對你好失望"},{"pid":"557a3e4d348b06250ac5f34f7b28bca3257e4804","tid":2063090,"uid":29929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"但吹叫雞sp有咩益處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244eafa6e8dadb39e0bb0db72d1bc7c7dffb9ab3","tid":2063090,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"A380毒撚"},{"pid":"f223fd249e1edec7617eb0286d1249125a94f3a4","tid":2063090,"uid":318946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"557a3e4d3